Shh.. I’m gonna spill some hair secrets for you! 

When I do a root touch up it’s important to treat your newly bleached roots kindly. It’s exactly why I choose @splathairdye not only because the color range is on point but because their formulas contain Baobab seed oil which moisturizes leaving your hair w/ a beautiful shine but also helps protect against UV rays! It’s also packed vitamins and minerals from the quinoa extract which helps prevent damage. 

🚨Hair Tip- for some added repair while I color I love to add a hair mask or deep conditioning treatment into my color which gives you room to play with the depth of the color and gives you instant repair. It’s a 2-4-1 I mean who doesn’t love to save time. I love using Splats conditioning gloss masque.

🚨 Hair dye Tip-  if you get color on your skin don’t fret it won’t last but the best way to get it off asap hot water on a wash cloth and scrub it off …. Voila
